    "In Preservation, Usability and user experience were used almost exclusively as the evaluation purposes.",
    "In terms of the type of questions, it is divided between Likert and Open, with slightly more emphasis on Likert.",
    "In Musealization, Usability and user experience remain the most common purpose, but Technology or System Application and Education/Engagement are added, each with a 20% usage rate.",
    "The type of question is somewhat more balanced, with a slightly higher usage of Open questions.",
    "Finally, the most balanced area of application is Education, with Usability and user experience having the same weight as Education/Engagement, each with a usage rate of approximately 40%."
